Class ParcelPlacement

java.lang.Object
com.bcs2024.knapsack.model.Parcel
com.bcs2024.knapsack.model.ParcelPlacement
public class ParcelPlacement extends Parcel
Represents the placement of a parcel within a cargo space, extending the Parcel class to include position and color information for visualization purposes.
